== Auth Flow Lifecycle ==
Provider/token combinations demonstrate success, retry, and failure paths.

-- Scenario 1: Steamworks success --
[auth] Steamworks [compatibility-only] dispatch (/steam/session/validate): submitting credential
[auth] Steamworks [compatibility-only] payload summary: ticket=TICKET-…cdef (len=23)
[auth] Steamworks [compatibility-only] result -> outcome=success, message="Steamworks heuristic compatibility backend accepted ticket (ticket=TICKET-…cdef)"

-- Scenario 2: Steamworks malformed --
[auth] Steamworks [compatibility-only] dispatch (/steam/session/validate): submitting credential
[auth] Steamworks [compatibility-only] payload summary: ticket=SHORT-TICKET (len=12)
[auth] Steamworks [compatibility-only] result -> outcome=failure, message="Steamworks heuristic compatibility backend rejected ticket: payload too short"

-- Scenario 3: Steamworks denied --
[auth] Steamworks [compatibility-only] dispatch (/steam/session/validate): submitting credential
[auth] Steamworks [compatibility-only] payload summary: ticket=TICKET-…6789 (len=24)
[auth] Steamworks [compatibility-only] result -> outcome=failure, message="Steamworks heuristic compatibility backend denied the ticket"

-- Scenario 4: Hybrid fallback --
[auth] Hybrid [compatibility-only] dispatch (/steam/session/validate): submitting credential
[auth] Hybrid [compatibility-only] payload summary: ticket=retry:T…FFFF (len=21)
[auth] Hybrid [compatibility-only] hybrid-fallback (/steam/session/validate): Steamworks heuristic compatibility backend returned retry; dispatching open adapter fallback
[auth] Open Steam Adapter [compatibility-only] dispatch (/launcher/auth/verify): submitting fallback credential
[auth] Hybrid [compatibility-only] result -> outcome=success, message="Hybrid fallback accepted credential via heuristic open adapter (token=retry:T…FFFF)"

-- Scenario 5: Open adapter refresh --
[auth] Open Steam Adapter [compatibility-only] dispatch (/launcher/auth/verify): submitting credential
[auth] Open Steam Adapter [compatibility-only] payload summary: token=JWT-abc…resh (len=18)
[auth] Open Steam Adapter [compatibility-only] result -> outcome=retry, message="Open adapter heuristic compatibility backend requested launcher token refresh"

-- Scenario 6: Open adapter revoked --
[auth] Open Steam Adapter [compatibility-only] dispatch (/launcher/auth/verify): submitting credential
[auth] Open Steam Adapter [compatibility-only] payload summary: token=TOKEN-r…7890 (len=23)
[auth] Open Steam Adapter [compatibility-only] result -> outcome=failure, message="Open adapter heuristic compatibility backend treated token as revoked"

-- Scenario 7: Open adapter success --
[auth] Open Steam Adapter [compatibility-only] dispatch (/launcher/auth/verify): submitting credential
[auth] Open Steam Adapter [compatibility-only] payload summary: token=TOKEN-V…7890 (len=22)
[auth] Open Steam Adapter [compatibility-only] result -> outcome=success, message="Open adapter heuristic compatibility backend accepted standalone token (token=TOKEN-V…7890)"
